<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7289> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7289" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut.? 46. See MRR 2.300. He had held offices earlier (Bell. Afr. 57.3). He may be identified with M. Aquinus (5; cf. 2), Leg., lieut. under Cassius in 43 and 42 (MRR 2.364, and insert him for 43 in 2.352). Appian's reference in BC 2.119 to an # who joined the liberators after the murder of Caesar favors the identification (TJC). On his coinage in 43-42, see Crawford, RRC 1.513, no. 498. See also Wiseman, NM 214, no. 36.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6181> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6181" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Cassius in 43 and 42 (Grueber, CRRBM 2.480)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5825> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5825" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "An officer, probably a Legate, since he was a senator, in the Pompeian forces in Africa (Bell. Afr. 57; 89.5)." .
